race.comment: ACCOUNTS MANAGER (5) scored two back then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 4 length 4th at The Meadows (30.69). Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. ANGRY MURRAY COD (2) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 2.25 lengths at Healesville in a handy 19.53 beating Blank Slate. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. One of main contenders. VIXEN FORCE (1) has struggled for best form recently, last time finishing 4th (24.61) in a Special conditions H at Bendigo. Has won here at this journey. Key runner on best form. Something for the Multiples: MAGIC BULLSEYE (8)
